  "title": "Project Engineer (Training Provided | Mechanical Engineering | Electrical Engineering)",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li><li><strong>Basic $3500 - $4000 + Completion Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: West (Company Transport Provided)</strong></li><li><strong>Working day: Monday to Friday</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: 8am to 5.10pm </strong></li><li><strong>ONE YEAR RENEWABLE CONTRACT </strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Plan and execute engineering projects within scope, budget, and timeline.</strong></li><li>Coordinate with internal teams, vendors and client to ensure smooth delivery.</li><li><strong>Review technical drawings and ensure compliance with standards and customer specification.</strong></li><li><strong>Monitor progress, prepare reports, and resolve technical issues.</strong></li><li>Source and procure of equipment require for project.</li><li>Site monitoring and coordination.</li><li>Other ad hoc duties as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess minimum Diploma or Degree in Mechanical, Electrical or related engineering field.</li><li><strong>Training will be provided for those without/lesser experience.</strong></li></ul><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)<br />EA Recruitment Pte Ltd<br />EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
